      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfb473b00a5c4fe1adf9c8b24a5f5b9e/c7314cd706928965-b4/s640x960/99cf5950b920ca9445d6919eef4c55325ae09731.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"804\" data-orig-width=\"1200\" alt=\"Image: The office of a chiropterologist*  &quot;His extreme immersion study technique amassed sensational insights into the lives of madagascar&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s fruit bats, but the professor himself was never quite the same again.&quot;  In the top right corner we can see the professor hanging upside down from a pipe near the ceiling, reading a book and eating an apple.  *bat scientist\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfb473b00a5c4fe1adf9c8b24a5f5b9e/c7314cd706928965-b4/s75x75_c1/455ff8145cbe42bd7ce5f98c34c5e6c1b74ef43d.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfb473b00a5c4fe1adf9c8b24a5f5b9e/c7314cd706928965-b4/s100x200/2d2a6e2d11e0570c943daabcc52ff601196515a2.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfb473b00a5c4fe1adf9c8b24a5f5b9e/c7314cd706928965-b4/s250x400/7348e8ee7424038c80eb1b3160ab10246dd66795.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfb473b00a5c4fe1adf9c8b24a5f5b9e/c7314cd706928965-b4/s400x600/cd2d685ddd6c20a3901f17d59b7c1e654b3623ba.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfb473b00a5c4fe1adf9c8b24a5f5b9e/c7314cd706928965-b4/s500x750/4b21c029c6cf36e07036bc0a7ce7c03faeade26d.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfb473b00a5c4fe1adf9c8b24a5f5b9e/c7314cd706928965-b4/s540x810/3421e3968550de351cdac1bd2035dff692e9903e.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfb473b00a5c4fe1adf9c8b24a5f5b9e/c7314cd706928965-b4/s640x960/99cf5950b920ca9445d6919eef4c55325ae09731.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/dfb473b00a5c4fe1adf9c8b24a5f5b9e/c7314cd706928965-b4/s1280x1920/07a500b301998c62637fe04121139c2d488a4e86.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/>"
