      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/3faf924c9341c065f38b4c325ddb1232/80fdc7e833ed1786-bf/s640x960/16295f3151a7227aac8f4465f497d87646dfc1de.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"816\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Title (in a yellow star): &quot;Offers at our Bookshop&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel 1: Buy two, get one free &#10;A figure approaches the till with three books&#10;&#10;Panel 2: Buy four, get a free tote bag&#10;The cashier holds up a tote.&#10;&#10;Panel 3: Buy one, get talking to staff, leave with five &#10;Customer leaved happily, carrying a full tote and waving to tthe wo staff &#10;&#10;Panel 4: Buy none, get a guilty feeling &#10;Customer skulks out of the shop&#10;&#10;Panel 5: Buy three as gifts, get the urge to keep them &#10;Customer walking home already reading the books&#10;&#10;Panel 6. Get overexcited, buy twelve...Get home, get eye-roll from partner&#10;Customer arrives home reading a book and carrying two full totes.&#10;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/3faf924c9341c065f38b4c325ddb1232/80fdc7e833ed1786-bf/s75x75_c1/f0d93af783d31d68869cb07e3ef2ce403381c7a3.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3faf924c9341c065f38b4c325ddb1232/80fdc7e833ed1786-bf/s100x200/45b54ef9dc39a54bf1e28034a943e92c8c216e4f.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3faf924c9341c065f38b4c325ddb1232/80fdc7e833ed1786-bf/s250x400/8a22af2da1c2476e6462bb5d72b4ac15769eb520.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3faf924c9341c065f38b4c325ddb1232/80fdc7e833ed1786-bf/s400x600/6ef25bd6729104b2a6ed1c21d3fccedc853f0a54.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3faf924c9341c065f38b4c325ddb1232/80fdc7e833ed1786-bf/s500x750/329aa12b3824f9b205e3686a31d232a2b960f31f.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3faf924c9341c065f38b4c325ddb1232/80fdc7e833ed1786-bf/s540x810/7e4f827ddbedbc041e2682865c06d655fe745989.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3faf924c9341c065f38b4c325ddb1232/80fdc7e833ed1786-bf/s640x960/16295f3151a7227aac8f4465f497d87646dfc1de.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3faf924