    {
      "id": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/821944325293457408",
      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/821944325293457408",
      "title": "My latest New Scientist cartoon. Many more here: https://www.newscientist.com/author/tom-gauld/",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/cfde7764cfe945de2eb7d9d3bbcca885/fb57bba270fc51b0-3b/s640x960/54b219549ae77def15d6fd40254f3e8a695b3a9b.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"799\" data-orig-width=\"1200\" alt=\"Title: My confidence in my understanding of the scientific theory.   A diagram where the confidence is marked in red on an otherwise white figure   Panel 1 &quot;Before I got a book about it.&quot; The figure is red up to about his stomach  Panel 2 &quot;While I was reading the book.&quot; The figure is reading a book. He is red up to his forehead.  Panel 3 &quot;When I had finished the book.&quot;  The red level has dropped  to around his mouth  Panel 4 &quot;One week later.&quot; Now it is at his chest.  Panel 5 &quot;When I try to explain it to somebody.&quot;  The level is back at stomach level.  Panel 6 &quot;When they ask a follow-up question.&quot; The red is so low we can barely see it.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/cfde7764cfe945de2eb7d9d3bbcca885/fb57bba270fc51b0-3b/s75x75_c1/dbe8663533ab056cf8e812548318bc297518208d.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cfde7764cfe945de2eb7d9d3bbcca885/fb57bba270fc51b0-3b/s100x200/ab0555035454ded815bedc6be3d0ca9673fcce70.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cfde7764cfe945de2eb7d9d3bbcca885/fb57bba270fc51b0-3b/s250x400/4fb91b9afb87bce20c12a339cbbb4e25540f32b2.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cfde7764cfe945de2eb7d9d3bbcca885/fb57bba270fc51b0-3b/s400x600/34bb0d1890dd34784d85cf19ddf4e25ee23e088a.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cfde7764cfe945de2eb7d9d3bbcca885/fb57bba270fc51b0-3b/s500x750/1c0e25ad7586fe0ad1b8b6c47354946fc9376691.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cfde7764cfe945de2eb7d9d3bbcca885/fb57bba270fc51b0-3b/s540x810/d044984328fb67d4114fa61867919c9a778f987f.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cfde7764cfe945de2eb7d9d3bbcca885/fb57bba270fc51b0-3b/s640x960/54b219549ae77def15d6fd40254f3e8a695b3a9b.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cfde7764cfe945de2eb7d9d3bbcca885/fb57bba270